    "Title": "RESOURCE DRIVE: DEFEND SMALL CARGO SHIP",
    "Description": "To all contractors with combat pilot experience: we need your help urgently.\n\nA small cargo vessel of ours is currently under fire from a group of outlaws at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>. We need a capable pilot to head out there and <EM4>help defend them as they prepare to quantum</EM4>.\n\nThey don\u2019t have much time. The resources they\u2019re carrying, however small, will make a difference in the UEE\u2019s call for resources. If they can deliver them, we\u2019ll be sure to compensate you appropriately.\n\n\nDenver Samuels\nContractor Liaison Officer\nCrusader Industries",
